            "title": "A股開跌  深股跌轉升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股早市窄幅爭持，深股跌轉升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬綜指開報3376點，跌4點或0.12%，一度升1點，現升0.35點或0.01%，報 3390點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深成指開報10210點，跌9點或0.09%。現升30點或0.28%，報10249。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300開報3910點，跌3點0.08%，現升3點或0.09%，報3917點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創板指數開報2043點，跌2點或0.1%，現升7點或0.36%，報2052點。</p>\n</div>",
